@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName monospace
skinparam padding 5

title Workflow 2: Local Buffer Scope (Micro)

actor User
participant "Unsaved Buffer" as Buffer
participant "LLM Agent" as LLM
participant "list_buffer_tags" as Tool2
participant "read_tag_source" as Tool3
collections "AST Engines" as Engines

User -> LLM : 1. Prompts with buffer name & issue
LLM -> Tool2 : 2. Requests buffer structural overview
Tool2 -> Engines : 3. Parses active buffer (Live)
Engines --> LLM : 4. Returns structural index
LLM -> Tool3 : 5. Requests specific function body
Tool3 -> Buffer : 6. Extracts exact live code
Tool3 --> LLM : 7. Returns live implementation
LLM --> User : 8. Delivers contextualized fix
@enduml